===============

Premium security  
at any scale
===============================

Per-seat pricing for projects and teams of all sizes—no hidden fees, no surprises.

Developer
---------

Secure your solo projects & focus on what matters - building.

Free for 3 users

$8/mo per additional user

*   Integrations
*   Doppler CLI for local development
*   Service tokens
*   Email alerts and recurring reminders
*   3 days of activity logs
*   Secrets referencing
*   Secret value types
    
*   API and webhooks access
*   Webhook logs
    
*   Config syncs (5)
    

[Start for Free](https://dashboard.doppler.com/register?plan=developer)

Most popular

Team
----

Unlock team productivity & protect shared secrets.

Free for 14 days

$21/mo per user

*   Change Requests
    
*   SAML SSO
*   Identity Based Authentication
*   Role-Based Access Controls
*   Integration Access Scoping
    
*   90 Days of activity logs
*   Automatic secret rotation
    
*   Service accounts
*   Config inheritance
*   Trusted IPs
*   Priority support
*   99.95% SLO
*   Config syncs (100)
    
*   Add-on enterprise features
    

[Start 14 Day Trial](https://dashboard.doppler.com/register?plan=team)

Enterprise
----------

Tailored to your compliance and regulatory needs.

Custom pricing

Scales with your team

*   Change Request Policies
    
*   Custom permissions & roles
*   User groups
*   Enterprise SCIM
*   Fully manage in Terraform
*   On-Prem secret rotation
    
*   Enterprise Key Management (EKM)
*   Dynamic secrets
*   SIEM Log Forwarding
    
*   Unlimited config syncs
*   Custom activity log retention
*   Custom rate limits
*   Enterprise support
*   Custom contract & invoicing
*   Dedicated account manager
*   Coming soon: Analytics dashboard

Return on investment

Pays for itself
---------------

How many developers work at your company? Use the slider below to see the estimated scope and impact of your secrets sprawl problem.

50 users

Salary

Estimated average salary of an engineer in your organization.

2 hours

Average hours recovered per developer per week. We do this by preventing missing and misconfigured secrets through secrets management.

$250,000

Estimated annual savings for your organization from eliminating secrets sprawl. Mitigated costs of prevented breaches compounds further savings.

Team Plan add-ons

Additional superpowers
----------------------

Is your team rapidly scaling but not ready to make the leap to enterprise? Purchase add-ons available on the Team plan to help support your growth.

Custom roles

**Additional $9/seat per month**

Tailor access through fine-grained workplace and project permission profiles. Apply custom roles to users and groups.

![Image 3](https://www.doppler.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2Fq3zajrd2%2Fproduction%2F0dffbca13c93c3b4c736a5836a8b144a0f4364d4-60x60.svg%3Ffit%3Dmax%26auto%3Dformat&w=3840&q=75)

User groups

**Additional $9/seat per month**

Assign users to groups with specific access levels, implementing the principle of least privilege for each project.

![Image 4](https://www.doppler.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2Fq3zajrd2%2Fproduction%2F0dffbca13c93c3b4c736a5836a8b144a0f4364d4-60x60.svg%3Ffit%3Dmax%26auto%3Dformat&w=3840&q=75)

Integration syncs

**Additional $9/seat per month**

Increase the sync limit from 100 to 500. Integration syncs are the connection between a config of secrets and your infrastructure.

![Image 5](https://www.doppler.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2Fq3zajrd2%2Fproduction%2F0dffbca13c93c3b4c736a5836a8b144a0f4364d4-60x60.svg%3Ffit%3Dmax%26auto%3Dformat&w=3840&q=75)

Open source

We love supporting the open source community through discounted rates and sponsorship.

[Unlock Discount](mailto:support@doppler.com)

Education

Tomorrow's engineers deserve amazing tools to manage and store their secrets today.

[Unlock Discount](mailto:support@doppler.com)

Non-profits

We are excited to support the companies making the world a better and safer place.

[Unlock Discount](mailto:support@doppler.com)

Agencies

Become an approved agency, technology partner, or professional services partner.

[Become a Partner](mailto:partnership@doppler.com)

![Image 6](https://www.doppler.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2Fq3zajrd2%2Fproduction%2F50ec844292688132e06e04718ad0febc3b22c69c-100x101.svg%3Ffit%3Dmax%26auto%3Dformat&w=3840&q=75)

1% of all subscriptions are donated to removing CO from the atmosphere

[Learn More](https://climate.stripe.com/SzzLAn)

FAQs
----

What does Doppler do?

Doppler's [secrets manager](https://www.doppler.com/platform/manage) empowers engineers and their teams to quickly set up a secure way to store and manage their sensitive application secrets like API keys, database urls, certifications, etc. through a dashboard, API, and command line tool.

How long does it take to learn Doppler?

Is Doppler secure? Where's my data stored?

How will you charge me?

What counts as a user?

Can I add an Enterprise feature to my Team subscription?

Do you offer a discount for non-profits, students, and educators?

Can I deploy Doppler on-premise?

Do I need a credit card to sign up?

How does Doppler pricing work?

How does billing work?

Can I cancel at anytime?

Enter the new era of secrets management
---------------------------------------

Trusted by the world’s best DevOps and security teams. Doppler is the secrets manager developers love.
